WEBVTT

00:00.014 --> 00:02.182
- Please don't tell me we're witches.
- We're witches.

00:02.210 --> 00:04.445
You have an enemy, Joanna,
and they're not gonna stop

00:04.478 --> 00:06.224
<i>until you
and your girls are dead.</i>

00:07.342 --> 00:11.302
- WENDY: The imposter... she stabbed me.
- I know who killed my husband.

00:11.303 --> 00:13.371
You are under arrest
for the murder of Bill Thatcher.

00:13.372 --> 00:14.879
Wait. Adam,
what the hell?!

00:14.913 --> 00:17.217
- Wendy?
- Ingrid, what were you thinking?

00:17.240 --> 00:20.285
You resurrect someone you love,
then someone you love has to die.

00:20.286 --> 00:23.995
INGRID: <i>Do you realize you were almost
burned alive and drowned all in one night?</i>

00:24.037 --> 00:26.154
Why was Mom arrested
for murder?

00:26.205 --> 00:28.073
The shape-shifter
that has it out for your mom

00:28.107 --> 00:31.426
<i>has taken your mom's form, killed Bill
Thatcher, leaving Maura as a witness.</i>

00:31.427 --> 00:33.857
- You have a brother?
- DASH: Yeah. I told you I had a brother.

00:33.875 --> 00:36.394
- I don't think you should be here.
- Definitely shouldn't be here.

00:36.395 --> 00:37.695
You're gonna need it
for when you leave town.

00:37.696 --> 00:38.887
Think I'll stay a while.

00:38.888 --> 00:41.291
Have you ever seen me
run away from a fight?

00:41.292 --> 00:45.287
We'll find the shifter, and we'll keep
the girls alive as long as we can.

