01:21.406 --> 01:23.457
(gasps loudly) Oh.

01:23.508 --> 01:26.293
Killian. Thank God.

01:26.298 --> 01:28.799
(sighs)

01:31.875 --> 01:34.652
Wendy? What are
you doing up?

01:34.653 --> 01:35.910
(sighs)

01:35.911 --> 01:38.556
Tarot cards like to be read
in the middle of the night,

01:38.557 --> 01:40.511
and I need them
to cooperate.

01:40.512 --> 01:44.449
I'm trying to find out who's gonna die
because of the curse that you unleashed.

01:44.585 --> 01:47.306
I thought you said
it wasn't possible to know.

01:47.307 --> 01:49.744
I did say that, didn't I?

01:49.745 --> 01:53.347
But you can't always believe
everything that I tell you.

01:54.673 --> 01:56.841
(gasps)

02:02.122 --> 02:04.840
(sighs)

02:06.126 --> 02:07.943
Oh.

02:16.195 --> 02:18.034
No...

02:18.870 --> 02:20.571
(sighs)

02:26.481 --> 02:29.845
- This can't be right.
- Who is it?

02:30.343 --> 02:31.977
Is it Mom...?

02:33.198 --> 02:35.533
Is it Freya?

02:36.105 --> 02:38.507
Oh, God, is it you...?

02:38.746 --> 02:41.639
According to these cards,
the person who's going to die...

02:42.312 --> 02:43.829
Is you.

02:43.863 --> 02:45.164
What?

02:45.198 --> 02:46.916
(whimpering)

02:48.184 --> 02:52.031
You have no idea how to actually get
to the kitchen from here, do you?

02:52.032 --> 02:54.814
Not really. This is why
I like living on a boat.

02:54.815 --> 02:57.564
It's impossible to get
lost going to the kitchen.

02:58.773 --> 03:00.207
(gasps)

03:06.937 --> 03:09.104
Mmm.

03:10.551 --> 03:12.468
Mmm. (footsteps
approaching)

03:12.469 --> 03:14.220
DASH:
Freya?

03:15.152 --> 03:17.766
- What the hell's going on?
- Dash.

03:18.883 --> 03:20.518
Wait!

03:21.007 --> 03:22.557
Dash?

03:22.789 --> 03:24.155
Help me...

03:24.156 --> 03:28.041
WENDY: I'm sorry, Ingrid, but
the truth is, you deserve this.

03:28.042 --> 03:30.127
This is all your fault.

03:30.128 --> 03:32.179
(whimpering)

03:32.180 --> 03:33.855
Dash?

03:33.957 --> 03:36.981
(sighs, panting)

03:51.047 --> 03:54.433
WOMAN (raspy):
Joanna?

03:55.503 --> 03:57.537
(guttural gasping)

03:58.402 --> 04:00.320
(groans, gasping)

04:00.510 --> 04:03.512
(guttural gasping)

04:03.726 --> 04:06.328
(gasps loudly)

04:06.363 --> 04:08.864
(sighs)

04:13.549 --> 04:16.651
(gasps)

04:17.908 --> 04:19.555
(sighs)

04:19.926 --> 04:21.125
(panting)

04:21.177 --> 04:23.045
(sighs)

04:23.079 --> 04:26.298
(gasps, sighs)

04:29.636 --> 04:31.186
(sighs)

04:32.296 --> 04:34.979
Season 1, Episode 3
"Today I Am a Witch"

04:35.101 --> 04:38.101
Sync & corrections: Reef
www.addic7ed.com

04:38.389 --> 04:42.053
- Can't sleep?
- Bad dream. You?

04:42.054 --> 04:43.989
I'm just looking
through some old spells,

04:44.023 --> 04:46.358
trying to find inspiration
for our shifter problem.

04:46.392 --> 04:48.107
- Any luck?
- Let me guess...

04:48.108 --> 04:50.263
You're worried about the price
for the resurrection spell.

04:50.264 --> 04:53.466
Maybe we could find a way
to reverse it so no one has to die.

04:53.467 --> 04:56.583
Ingrid, honey, we've gone over this.
There's nothing we can do.

04:56.584 --> 04:58.906
Balance has to be restored.
We can't change that.

04:58.907 --> 05:01.958
But I can't just sit around
waiting for someone I love to die

05:01.959 --> 05:03.745
because of my stupid mistake.

05:03.746 --> 05:05.479
You don't have
to just sit around.

05:05.480 --> 05:08.490
Let me teach you. There's still
so much for you to learn.

05:08.491 --> 05:11.660
I don't want to learn
anything else about magic.

05:11.661 --> 05:13.579
Don't be so sure about that.

05:16.605 --> 05:19.058
Magic is what
you make of it.

05:19.059 --> 05:23.356
It can be dangerous and deadly,
or it can be mystical and beautiful.

05:23.813 --> 05:26.097
It's up to you.

05:27.283 --> 05:28.933
(door opening)

05:29.614 --> 05:31.046
Huh.

05:32.837 --> 05:34.537
Am I missing something?

05:34.538 --> 05:36.466
- Nope.
- What are you doing here?

05:36.492 --> 05:39.741
Shouldn't you be at Fair Haven
with your dashing fiancÃ©?

05:39.764 --> 05:42.968
I can't sleep. Every night,
it's the same thing.

05:42.969 --> 05:45.712
I have the hottest, most
incredible sex with Killian.

05:45.713 --> 05:46.849
- Nice.
- What?!

05:46.850 --> 05:48.267
In my dreams.
Only in my dreams.

05:48.268 --> 05:50.419
In real life, I have that kind
of sex with Dash.

05:50.420 --> 05:52.198
Yes, we know.
We all know.

05:52.199 --> 05:54.412
Every time he sleeps over, like,
three, four times a night.

05:54.413 --> 05:56.480
- Really? Four times? Oh...
- Mm-hmm.

05:56.481 --> 05:59.612
The point is, it's not like there's
a problem with me and Dash,

05:59.613 --> 06:01.838
but I can't make
these Killian dreams stop.

06:01.901 --> 06:04.135
It's like, I feel guilty,
like I'm cheating,

06:04.153 --> 06:05.904
and I'm not even doing anything.

06:05.938 --> 06:07.767
I need to get him
out of my head.

06:07.768 --> 06:10.587
I'm a witch now. How hard can it
be to control my own thoughts?

06:10.616 --> 06:12.250
- Very hard.
- Very hard.

06:13.096 --> 06:14.704
Look, girls, take it easy.

06:14.705 --> 06:17.315
You can't master the art
of witchcraft in a week.

06:17.316 --> 06:18.974
But don't worry.
It'll take time,

06:18.975 --> 06:21.018
but I can teach you
everything you need to know.

06:21.019 --> 06:23.121
Let me be your Mr. Miyagi.

06:23.122 --> 06:24.997
Just, please
don't tell your mother.

06:24.998 --> 06:26.596
Please don't tell your mother
what?

06:26.597 --> 06:28.561
- Nothing.
- Nothing?

06:28.562 --> 06:30.820
Hey, I don't want
the girls doing magic.

06:30.821 --> 06:33.145
- It's too dangerous.
- Okay.

06:33.146 --> 06:35.079
We're not kids in
pigtails anymore.

06:35.080 --> 06:37.056
We're adults who can
make our own decisions.

06:37.057 --> 06:38.825
Ooh, I miss the pigtails.

06:38.826 --> 06:40.360
I do, I do.

06:40.374 --> 06:43.041
Oh, it's not
about grown-up or not.

06:43.042 --> 06:45.364
I've just... I've been alive
a lot longer than you.

06:45.365 --> 06:48.077
I know things you don't.
It's for your own good.

06:48.078 --> 06:50.925
But maybe we could help you
with the shape-shifter.

06:51.067 --> 06:53.735
There is no shape-shifter
anymore.

06:53.736 --> 06:55.353
Everything is under control.

06:55.354 --> 06:57.394
I took care of it
with a banishing spell.

06:57.395 --> 07:00.564
Whoever it is, they can't
come anywhere near us.

07:00.733 --> 07:03.541
And I don't think we want
any temptation around.

07:03.542 --> 07:06.193
Right? Now, well,
just to be safe.

07:06.249 --> 07:07.763
(gasping)

07:07.764 --> 07:09.537
- What are you doing?!
- What the hell?!

07:09.540 --> 07:10.873
That's an heirloom.

07:12.254 --> 07:14.706
- Now it's ash.
- Wha...?

07:14.724 --> 07:16.441
Good night.

07:23.970 --> 07:26.171
What the hell
happened here?

07:28.549 --> 07:31.685
What a minute. I've seen that
symbol before. <i>Malus Amplio?</i>

07:31.719 --> 07:35.823
It draws in dark energy,
and magnifies the power of evil.

07:35.824 --> 07:38.834
It was in the ground where
Bill Thatcher was killed,

07:38.835 --> 07:40.786
in my dream last night,
and now, it's here.

07:40.787 --> 07:43.747
And you can't think of anyone who would
want to do something like this to you?

07:43.748 --> 07:46.175
I'm immortal. I can think
of too many people.

07:46.176 --> 07:47.701
That's the problem.

07:47.702 --> 07:49.703
So let me help you.

07:49.737 --> 07:52.064
Would you be willing to
serve as a character witness?

07:52.065 --> 07:53.590
That's not what I meant,
and you know it.

07:53.624 --> 07:56.843
I know, but I'm not using
dark magic to get out of this.

07:56.844 --> 07:58.831
Sadly, that's the only
magic that would work.

07:58.832 --> 08:02.041
Is it possible that you've gotten more
stubborn over the last hundred years?

08:02.042 --> 08:05.494
Just because I'm not dealing with this
in the way that you want me to...

08:05.495 --> 08:07.909
You're not dealing
with this at all, Jo.

08:07.922 --> 08:09.787
And you lied to the girls
last night,

08:09.788 --> 08:11.867
telling them that
you banished the shape-shifter.

08:11.868 --> 08:13.769
That's not possible.
You don't know who it is.

08:13.770 --> 08:15.562
I lied so they don't have
to worry,

08:15.563 --> 08:17.864
so that they can get back
to their carefree, normal lives.

08:17.865 --> 08:21.699
Things are not going back to
the way they were! That's over.

08:21.700 --> 08:23.558
The girls know
who they are.

08:23.568 --> 08:25.352
Their powers are only going
to get stronger.

08:25.360 --> 08:27.823
We need to be able to teach them
how to control their gifts,

08:27.824 --> 08:30.377
so they don't hurt someone
or themselves.

08:30.411 --> 08:33.278
You said that you would
help me keep them alive.

08:33.765 --> 08:36.462
That means keeping
them away from magic.

08:38.419 --> 08:41.160
All right, yeah.
Whatever you say.

08:41.162 --> 08:43.163
No magic.

08:45.407 --> 08:47.708
- Whoa...
- Oh, wow. That was so cool.

08:47.709 --> 08:50.339
That was nothing. Wait till you
girls see what I can teach you.

08:50.340 --> 08:53.733
We witches have way more talents
than just spell casting.

08:53.768 --> 08:57.572
Telekinesis, healing powers,
limited weather control.

08:57.573 --> 09:00.106
- We can control the weather?!
- She said "limited."

09:00.107 --> 09:03.647
(thunder crackling,
gasping)

09:03.648 --> 09:05.232
Limited, but still pretty cool.

09:05.233 --> 09:06.983
- How did you do that?
- Wow.

09:06.984 --> 09:08.534
Oh, we all work
in different ways.

09:08.535 --> 09:11.576
I'm ruled by instinct, so,
my powers come from the gut.

09:11.584 --> 09:15.105
Freya, you're ruled by emotion,
so, yours come from the heart.

09:15.154 --> 09:19.170
With practice, you're gonna be able
to read people's deepest desires,

09:19.171 --> 09:21.659
mix potions to make
them fall in love...

09:21.660 --> 09:23.235
- Or fall into bed...
- Really?

09:23.243 --> 09:25.805
Her specialty is sex.
I wouldn't have guessed that.

09:25.806 --> 09:28.492
Oh, really? Well,
what's her specialty? Reading?

09:28.493 --> 09:31.403
Kind of. Ingrid's powers
come from up here.

09:31.404 --> 09:34.507
Strength of mind,
intellect, invention.

09:34.508 --> 09:38.633
Watching you write a spell was like
watching Mozart compose a concerto.

09:38.641 --> 09:41.898
Wait a minute. So I can actually
come up with new spells,

09:41.949 --> 09:43.817
and not just read
old ones in books?

09:43.851 --> 09:45.785
Don't get any ideas.
You're still a novice.

09:45.820 --> 09:49.122
It's gonna take years of learning before
you can even think of writing a spell.

09:49.156 --> 09:51.013
So, what's Mom's
specialty?

09:51.014 --> 09:53.527
Everything. She's
the total package.

09:53.528 --> 09:57.063
When your mom's at full strength,
it's like there's nothing she can't do.

09:57.098 --> 10:00.271
So, can she teach me the spell
that'll get Killian out of my head?

10:00.297 --> 10:03.207
Oh, my God. Between the two of you,
it's like you've been given

10:03.208 --> 10:06.428
a brand-new toolbox with hundreds
of tools you've never seen before,

10:06.429 --> 10:08.606
all you want to do
is use a hammer.

10:08.607 --> 10:12.742
All right, Freya, I want you to try
to skip this stone on the water.

10:12.743 --> 10:13.945
Okay.

10:13.946 --> 10:17.115
Not with your hand.
With your mind.

10:19.507 --> 10:22.509
And, girls, remember,
this is just between us.

10:22.510 --> 10:24.468
We know. We can't tell
anyone we're witches.

10:24.469 --> 10:27.086
No. That, too. But don't tell your
mother that we're doing this,

10:27.087 --> 10:29.414
because she would freak
if you're doing magic.

10:46.931 --> 10:48.798
(hinges creak)

10:58.726 --> 11:01.027
(hinges creak)

11:09.532 --> 11:11.504
(groans)
It isn't working.

11:11.539 --> 11:13.485
Clear your mind.
Concentrate.

11:13.486 --> 11:15.949
Think of nothing else
but what you're trying to do.

11:15.950 --> 11:17.827
(exhales):
Okay.

11:17.878 --> 11:20.413
