11:20.448 --> 11:21.998
(deep burbling)

11:26.504 --> 11:28.433
(gasps) What happened?
Did it move?

11:28.434 --> 11:30.884
Yeah. If you were trying
to sink it, you did great.

11:30.885 --> 11:32.293
I suck at this.

11:32.294 --> 11:36.392
Freya, it takes practice; be patient.
All right, Ingrid, your turn.

11:36.393 --> 11:39.113
Same goes for you...
be patient, clear your mind.

11:39.114 --> 11:43.019
I want you to concentrate on dragging
the rock up out of the lake.

11:43.070 --> 11:45.105
(burbling)

11:47.368 --> 11:48.785
(gasps)

11:51.104 --> 11:52.774
(gasps)

11:53.428 --> 11:55.896
I was just trying
to lift the rock.

