meet in the middle?

39:35.563 --> 39:38.315
Works for me.

39:39.121 --> 39:41.351
So you can keep teaching
them, and I will, too.

39:41.369 --> 39:43.904
- I didn't...
- Oh, please!

39:43.955 --> 39:47.690
