off without a few lessons from you?

39:47.713 --> 39:49.543
I think I know my
sister pretty well.

39:49.577 --> 39:51.903
INGRID: Hey, Mom.
Are you okay?

39:51.904 --> 39:53.962
I am. I am.

39:53.965 --> 39:59.586
I have been doing a lot of thinking
about you girls being witches.

39:59.638 --> 40:01.472
It is who you are.

40:01.506 --> 40:03.474
It's who you've always been,

40:03.508 --> 40:06.543
